TREAT HIS BODY WITH CARE AND RESPECT.

13:06.053 --> 13:07.955
AND WE HAVE THE
UTMOST CONFIDENCE

13:07.988 --> 13:10.257
IN LENNOX'S COMPATIBILITY
WITH AIDEN AS A LOVER.

13:11.391 --> 13:14.094
ARE YOU GUYS KIDDING
ME RIGHT NOW?

13:14.127 --> 13:15.963
YOU'RE BOTH NUTS,
DO YOU KNOW THAT?

13:15.996 --> 13:18.298
WHEN MY FOLKS FOUND OUT
MY SISTER WAS HAVING SEX,

13:18.331 --> 13:20.267
