UM, HI. WHAT ARE YOU GUYS DOING?

13:28.008 --> 13:31.879
- IT'S NOT ABOUT WHAT WE'RE DOING.
- IT'S ABOUT WHAT YOU'RE DOING.

13:38.986 --> 13:41.154
NOW SEE? THAT'S PERMISSION.

13:52.900 --> 13:54.267
SO THIS IS IT, HUH?

13:54.301 --> 13:56.303
WE'RE JUST GONNA BE
STANDING DOWN HERE

13:56.336 --> 13:58.939
WHILE THEY'RE UP
THERE POTENTIALLY...

13:58.972 --> 14:01.641
HAVING S-S-S...

14:01.674 --> 14:04.277
IT'S LIKE WATCHING ADULT MOVIE
FROM OUTSIDE THE THEATER.

14:06.179 --> 14:07.948
WHAT ELSE CAN WE DO?

14:07.981 --> 14:09.917
WE'RE GONNA STOP
'EM, THAT'S WHAT.

14:09.950 --> 14:11.919
NO NO NO, JOE, YOU CAN'T.

14:11.952 --> 14:13.954
LOOK, DID YOUR PARENTS
EVER SAY ANYTHING

14:13.987 --> 14:16.189
THAT STOPPED YOU FROM DOING
SOMETHING YOU REALLY WANTED TO DO?

14:16.223 --> 14:19.326
BUT, MEL...

14:21.661 --> 14:23.196
I HATE THIS.

14:25.232 --> 14:27.200
DID I JUST HEAR A BED SQUEAK?

14:28.969 --> 14:31.038
- I GOT TO GET OUT OF HERE.
- JOE.

14:31.071 --> 14:33.073
JOE, HOLD ON.

14:33.106 --> 14:34.908
HOW FAR ARE YOU GOING?

14:34.942 --> 14:37.110
I WAS THINKING,
LIKE, UM, MICHIGAN.

14:37.144 --> 14:39.646
WE CAN'T. WE HAVE TO BE HERE

14:39.679 --> 14:42.249
- IN CASE THEY NEED US.
- NEED US? FOR WHAT, HUH?

14:42.282 --> 14:44.317
HELPFUL TIPS? SOME ENERGY BARS?

14:44.351 --> 14:45.986
- SIT.
- NO.

14:46.019 --> 14:47.420
- SIT.
- NO.

14:47.454 --> 14:49.456
ALL RIGHT, FINE. I'LL SIT.

14:49.489 --> 14:52.325
YOU KNOW WHAT? I'M GONNA
STAY, BUT I'M GONNA STAND.

14:52.359 --> 14:54.461
FINE. BE AS UNCOMFORTABLE
AS YOU WANT.

14:54.494 --> 14:56.997
I DON'T... I DON'T THINK

14:57.030 --> 14:58.698
I COULD BE ANY MORE
UNCOMFORTABLE, BURKE.

14:58.731 --> 15:01.969
I THINK YOU'LL FEEL A LITTLE BETTER
ONCE YOU'VE HAD SOME MEDICINE.

15:02.002 --> 15:04.504
- MEDICINE?
- YEAH, RED OR WHITE?

15:10.177 --> 15:14.247
THERE YOU GO. THIS IS GOING TO
MAKE YOUR FACE SOFT AND SMOOTH.

15:19.219 --> 15:22.956
WHA... YOU'RE GONNA SHAVE MY
FACE WITH THAT LADY RAZOR?

15:22.990 --> 15:24.992
UH-HUH.

15:25.025 --> 15:27.027
NOW TILT YOUR HEAD BACK.

15:27.060 --> 15:30.130
( hyperventilating )

15:30.163 --> 15:33.033
- RYDER, RELAX.
- SORRY.

15:33.066 --> 15:36.103
SORRY, I CAN'T HELP IT. IT'S LIKE YOU'RE
HOLDING A LITTLE PINK BUTCHER KNIFE.

15:36.136 --> 15:38.005
OKAY, ON THREE. READY?

15:38.038 --> 15:41.308
- ONE, TWO...
- AUGH!

15:41.341 --> 15:43.276
...THREE.

15:45.178 --> 15:48.048
OKAY, HERE WE GO.

15:48.081 --> 15:51.284
YUP. YUP YUP.

15:58.091 --> 15:59.993
- THIS IS ALL GOOD.
- YEAH.

16:00.027 --> 16:02.062
THERE'S NOTHING NOT
GOOD ABOUT IT.

16:07.334 --> 16:09.502
- ( thuds )
- OH!

16:09.536 --> 16:12.739
SORRY. SORRY. I'M REALLY SORRY.

16:12.772 --> 16:15.442
I'M OKAY. I'M OKAY.

16:19.779 --> 16:22.315
AM I CRUSHING YOUR LEG?

16:22.349 --> 16:24.384
- NO.
- GOOD.

16:27.154 --> 16:29.456
MMM... OW OW. CRUSHING
SOMETHING ELSE.

16:33.126 --> 16:36.029
I GOTTA TELL YOU, BURKE, YOU'VE
REALLY SHOWN INCREDIBLE RESTRAINT

16:36.063 --> 16:37.164
AND STRENGTH DURING
THIS WHOLE SITUATION.

16:37.197 --> 16:39.199
- REALLY?
- YEAH.

16:39.232 --> 16:42.035
YOU KNOW, FOR NOT BEING
AN ACTUAL PARENT,

16:42.069 --> 16:44.304
YOU'RE ACTUALLY... YOU'RE
A PRETTY GOOD ONE.

16:44.337 --> 16:47.807
I GUESS I AM GETTING
THE HANG OF IT.

16:47.840 --> 16:50.043
- ( chuckles )
- AND YOU...

16:50.077 --> 16:53.546
- YOU DID NOT KILL ANYBODY.
- ( both chuckle )

16:53.580 --> 16:55.215
THANK YOU FOR NOTICING.

16:57.250 --> 16:59.486
HOW YOU DOING ON THE MEDS?

16:59.519 --> 17:01.188
DOSE ME.

17:01.221 --> 17:03.156
STAT.

17:03.823 --> 17:05.825
THIS ISN'T WORKING, IS IT?

17:05.858 --> 17:07.560
NOT REALLY.

17:07.594 --> 17:09.429
IT'S WEIRD.

17:09.462 --> 17:11.464
YOU CAN HEAR THEM WATCHING US

17:11.498 --> 17:15.368
AND WAITING AND
CONDONING OUR BEHAVIOR.

17:15.402 --> 17:18.405
I FEEL LIKE WE'RE THE
LAST TWO ZOO PANDAS.

17:19.472 --> 17:21.508
I'M SORRY.

17:21.541 --> 17:24.411
I JUST DON'T REALLY WANT
TO DO THIS RIGHT NOW.

17:24.444 --> 17:26.846
I KNOW. ALL THIS ACCEPTANCE

17:26.879 --> 17:29.316
IS MAKING ME FEEL SO DIRTY.

17:29.349 --> 17:32.152
I SHOULD GO HOME.

17:35.655 --> 17:38.591
WAIT! NO, IF MY AUNT
SEES YOU LEAVE,

17:38.625 --> 17:41.494
THERE WILL BE ALL KINDS OF
QUESTIONS, POSSIBLY A SURVEY.

17:41.528 --> 17:44.097
JUST SNEAK OUT THE WINDOW.

17:44.131 --> 17:46.133
YEAH, TRUST ME. IT'LL
BE EASIER THAT WAY.

17:49.269 --> 17:50.870
IT'S KIND OF A LONG WAY DOWN.

17:50.903 --> 17:55.242
YOU'D RATHER HAVE AN AWKWARD
CONVERSATION WITH MY AUNT?

17:55.275 --> 17:57.210
SEE YA.

18:01.181 --> 18:05.118
HEY, IT'S LENNOX.

18:05.152 --> 18:06.586
HOW WAS THE...

18:06.619 --> 18:08.521
HOW DID YOU...

18:08.555 --> 18:11.324
HEY, IT'S LENNOX.

18:13.160 --> 18:15.128
NOTHING HAPPENED.

18:15.162 --> 18:16.863
YEAH, MY FIRST TIME
WAS LIKE THAT TOO.

18:16.896 --> 18:19.266
DON'T WORRY. IT GETS BETTER.

18:19.299 --> 18:22.335
NO, I MEAN, LITERALLY
NOTHING HAPPENED.

18:22.369 --> 18:25.205
ALL WE DID WAS KISS. AIDEN
WENT HOME HOURS AGO.

18:25.238 --> 18:27.307
WHAT? WHY?

18:27.340 --> 18:30.243
I DON'T KNOW. I MEAN, HAVING ALL
THESE ADULTS AND PARENTS KNOW

18:30.277 --> 18:32.179
AND EVERYTHING WAS
KIND OF A MOOD-KILLER.

18:32.212 --> 18:35.648
OH, I'M SORRY IF I WAS TOO...

18:35.682 --> 18:38.685
INTRUSIVE? NOSEY?

18:38.718 --> 18:40.453
I WAS GONNA SAY LOVING.

18:41.721 --> 18:43.323
LOOK, I KNOW I CAN'T LOCK
YOU UP IN A TOWER...

18:43.356 --> 18:46.159
JOE'S LOOKED INTO IT.

18:46.193 --> 18:48.328
I JUST WANNA KNOW WHAT'S
GOING ON BECAUSE I CARE.

18:48.361 --> 18:52.265
I DIDN'T WANT THIS EXPERIENCE
TO BE A BAD MEMORY SOME DAY.

18:52.299 --> 18:55.235
OR IN NINE MONTHS.

18:55.268 --> 18:57.504
SORRY IF I WAS UNCOOL.

18:57.537 --> 19:00.707
NO, IT'S NOT UNCOOL.
IT'S LOVING.

19:00.740 --> 19:03.210
- MMM!
- ( chuckles )

19:06.946 --> 19:09.449
- JOE.
- WHAT? WHAT HAPPENED?

19:09.482 --> 19:11.484
NOTHING.

19:11.518 --> 19:13.320
NOTHING?

19:13.353 --> 19:15.188
NOTHING.

19:15.222 --> 19:18.225
APPARENTLY OUR UNDERSTANDING
AND LOVING PRESENCE

19:18.258 --> 19:19.592
KILLED THE MOOD.

19:19.626 --> 19:22.562
THEY DIDN'T DO IT.

19:22.595 --> 19:25.465
♪ THEY DIDN'T DO IT, OH,
THEY DIDN'T DO IT ♪

19:25.498 --> 19:27.334
♪ OH, THEY DIDN'T DO IT.

19:27.367 --> 19:30.237
THIS IS AWESOME. THIS CALLS FOR
A CELEBRATION. YOU KNOW WHAT?

19:30.270 --> 19:32.339
I AM BREAKING OUT THE GOOD MEDS.

19:32.372 --> 19:35.308
- UH-OH.
- WHAT?

19:35.342 --> 19:38.578
- OH, THIS IS BAD.
- NO NO NO NO NO.

19:38.611 --> 19:40.213
THIS IS... THIS IS...
THIS IS GOOD.

19:40.247 --> 19:42.449
THIS IS GOOD. WE WERE AT BAD.
NOW WE'RE AT GOOD.

19:42.482 --> 19:45.485
- I LIKE GOOD.
- NOW WE DON'T KNOW WHEN IT'S GONNA HAPPEN,

19:45.518 --> 19:47.520
OR WITH WHO!

19:47.554 --> 19:50.490
IT COULD BE SOME DIRTBAG BASS
PLAYER IN AN OLD CAMPER SHELL.

19:50.523 --> 19:53.260
- IT'S LIKE YOU SAID...
- FEAR OF THE UNKNOWN?

19:53.293 --> 19:55.262
MMM! FEAR OF THE UNKNOWN.

19:56.796 --> 19:58.631
I'M GONNA BE DOING
A LOT OF RUNNING.

20:05.037 --> 20:08.775
- YOU JUST, UH, SHAVE?
- YEAH.

20:08.808 --> 20:11.678
- FIRST TIME?
- YEAH.

20:12.812 --> 20:15.248
AW, MY LITTLE
NEPHEW'S GROWING UP.

20:15.282 --> 20:18.251
( sniffs ) WHAT'S THAT
AFTERSHAVE YOU HAVE ON?

20:18.285 --> 20:20.753
YOUR FACE SMELLS LIKE
STRAWBERRIES AND JASMINE.

20:20.787 --> 20:23.323
SO DOES HOLLY'S.

20:23.356 --> 20:26.293
HEYYY!

20:26.326 --> 20:28.361
- DOUBLE STANDARD?
- YOU KNOW IT, BABY.

20:32.732 --> 20:35.368
WE JUST THINK THE KIDS SHOULD
HAVE ANOTHER GO AT IT.

20:37.570 --> 20:40.440
WE SENSE THEY MIGHT
HAVE FELT BLOCKED.

20:40.473 --> 20:43.543
BLOCKED. YEAH, THAT'S EXACTLY
WHAT I WAS GOING FOR.

20:43.576 --> 20:45.712
WELL, I THINK AFTER A
MISFIRE LIKE THAT,

20:45.745 --> 20:47.714
IT'S GOOD TO GET RIGHT
BACK UP ON THE HORSE.

20:47.747 --> 20:49.716
SEXUALLY SPEAKING.

20:51.584 --> 20:54.687
UH, SO YOU'RE CALLING
MY NIECE A HORSE?

20:54.721 --> 20:57.557
JOE, THEY'RE ALL YOURS.

20:57.590 --> 20:59.726
WHY THANK YOU, MEL.

20:59.759 --> 21:02.795
UH, LISTEN, I THINK THAT YOU
TWO SHOULD PROBABLY BE LEAVING

21:02.829 --> 21:05.698
BEFORE I DO SOMETHING TO YOU...

21:06.733 --> 21:08.868
THAT, UH, LANDS ME IN JAIL.

21:12.705 --> 21:14.674
I AGREE.
